{"tid":1459740,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有一個小建議，做到既話黑警就無可能喺機場清場，只需小部份人做就OK","createTime":"2019-08-12T19:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T00:10:22.000Z","uid":69334,"like":28,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc34fe8241d7d261ed845f69b59db71a4c2b854","tid":1459740,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:49:27.000Z","msg":"大家都知黑警鍾意依家鍾意玩滲透，我相信大家都明白以眼還眼既道理。<br />\n<br />\n但唔係叫大家cosplay警犬，而係cosplay旅客。只要現場有5至10%人，有帶個細gip仔，坐喺度乜都唔做就得，佢都肯定唔到你係咪真係旅客。最好個gip仲有埋寄倉用果啲紙條啦，懶閪香港人多數去完旅行返黎都唔會meet走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外，做得旅客就無必要著黑衫啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有疑似犬隻同你講野，你未話「sorry i dont know 廣東話」囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹閪得你漲咩<br />\n<br />\n如果想draw 傳媒attetion既話，未擺張banner喺側邊寫住「Dont shoot! I am pending for departure」囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a7ae022f22b8864cc2c4ac8975ae8116b88fc3","tid":1459740,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f8bb6485287fa10d462444fa22a97be29640ba","tid":1459740,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffd623278a3a24f880bad0bf024ed1e0d27213d","tid":1459740,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab1d5e5229a4fcf951e22e90429b053b4397c46","tid":1459740,"uid":179630,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019